From teenage sweethearts to life partners, there’s never been a dull moment with you.
We’ve built everything we once dreamt of - if you know, you know.
Through every high and low, we’ve held on with love, laughter, and an unshakeable bond.
We’ve lived fully, travelled endlessly, and created a little world of our own - our safe haven, our home.
Grateful for the love we share, the life we’ve built, and the memories yet to come.
Happy Anniversary, my love♥️forever isn’t long enough with you✨
